<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
When 'result' is non-zero the ternary evaluates to the left operand and the statement becomes an assignment of 'result' to itself (result = result). That write is executed but has no effect on program behaviour (no side-effects), so it is dead code. In other words, the branch that performs the self-assignment is redundant; the intention is clearly to call metal_uio_read_map_attr only when result is zero, but the current expression still performs a meaningless assignment in the non-zero case.
</scenario>
